import React from 'react';
import { styled } from '@mui/material/styles';
import Box from '@mui/material/Box';
import Grid from '@mui/material/Grid';
import Paper from '@mui/material/Paper';
import { useSelector, useDispatch } from 'react-redux';

const Item = styled(Paper)(({ theme }) => ({
    backgroundColor: theme.palette.mode === 'dark' ? '#1A2027' : '#fff',
    ...theme.typography.body2,
    padding: theme.spacing(1),
    fontWeight: '800',
    transition: '0.5s',
    height: 'calc((100vh - 144px)/7)',
    '&:hover':{
        cursor: 'pointer',
        backgroundColor:'#f1d5ba'
    },
    color: theme.palette.text.secondary
}));

const DayItem = styled(Paper)(({ theme }) => ({
    backgroundColor: 'rgb(25, 118, 210)',
    fontWeight: '600',
    ...theme.typography.body2,
    padding: theme.spacing(1),
    textAlign: 'center',
    transition: '0.5s',
    height: '1',
    color: 'white'
}));

function FormRow(props) {
    let weekDays = props.weekDay;

    return (
      <React.Fragment>
        <Grid item xs={0.8}>
          <DayItem elevation={6}>{props.weekDayName}</DayItem>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={1.7}>
          <Item elevation={6}>{weekDays[0].toString()}</Item>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={1.7}>
          <Item elevation={6}>{weekDays[1].toString()}</Item>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={1.7}>
          <Item elevation={6}>{weekDays[2].toString()}</Item>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={1.7}>
          <Item elevation={6}>{weekDays[3].toString()}</Item>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={1.7}>
          <Item elevation={6}>{weekDays[4].toString()}</Item>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={1.7}>
          <Item elevation={6}>{weekDays[5].toString()}</Item>
        </Grid>
      </React.Fragment>
    );
  }

function CalendarMonth(props) {
    const calendarObject = useSelector((state) => state.date.calendarObject);

    let sundays = calendarObject.filter((item) => {
        item.weekDay = 0;
    });
    return (
        <Box sx={{
            width: '100%',
            height: '100%',
            margin: '14px 0px 0px 0px'
            }}>
        <Grid
            container
            spacing={0.5}
            direction="row"
            sx={{ margin: '0px' }}>
            <Grid
                container
                xs={1.7}
                direction="column"
                item spacing={0.5}>
                <FormRow
                    weekDayName="Sunday"
                    weekDay={[26, 2, 9, 16, 23, 30]}/>
            </Grid>
            <Grid
                container
                xs={1.7}
                direction="column"
                item spacing={0.5}>
                <FormRow
                    weekDayName="Monday"
                    weekDay={[27, 3, 10, 17, 24, 1]}/>
            </Grid>
            <Grid
                container
                xs={1.7}
                direction="column"
                item spacing={0.5}>
                <FormRow
                    weekDayName="Tuesday"
                    weekDay={[28, 4, 11, 18, 25, 2]}/>
            </Grid>
            <Grid
                container
                xs={1.7}
                direction="column"
                item spacing={0.5}>
                <FormRow
                    weekDayName="Wednesday"
                    weekDay={[29, 5, 12, 19, 26, 3]}/>
            </Grid>
            <Grid
                container
                xs={1.7}
                direction="column"
                item spacing={0.5}>
                <FormRow
                    weekDayName="Thursday"
                    weekDay={[30, 6, 13, 20, 27, 4]}/>
            </Grid>
            <Grid
                container
                xs={1.7}
                direction="column"
                item spacing={0.5}>
                <FormRow
                    weekDayName="Friday"
                    weekDay={[31, 7, 14, 21, 28, 5]}/>
            </Grid>
            <Grid
                container
                xs={1.7}
                direction="column"
                item spacing={0.5}>
                <FormRow
                    weekDayName="Saturday"
                    weekDay={[1, 8, 15, 22, 29, 6]}/>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    </Box>
  )
}

export default CalendarMonth;
